{"type": "article", "id": 13556, "title": "还记得秋冬男装周吗，你可以按照这几个潮流买衣服了", "description": "时尚潮流这种事，挑自己喜欢的就好", "date": "2015-08-17T08:11:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6210, "name": "夹克"}, {"id": 11718, "name": "印花"}, {"id": 14579, "name": "高领衫"}, {"id": 1466, "name": "Hermès"}, {"id": 2114, "name": "Bottega Veneta"}, {"id": 3112, "name": "Bally"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162548QG3hXFy7Ll2JYa6N.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t夏天夏天悄悄过去，转眼 8 月过去一半了。站在夏天的尾巴上，各位美男子，你们是不是该准备秋装了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t作为对本季潮流的预告，可以回头去看年初的几场秋冬男装秀。虽然众多品牌将“女装男穿”这一趋势发挥到极致，而且因为是秀场，难免夸张。但也有一些好看又百搭的单品、趋势值得借鉴。\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t高领衫：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162532rmCDo6qiGTZulSWL.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Bally</em> &amp; <em>Bottega Veneta </em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162533ungPMTkdJ1AiZS5q.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"542\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Margaret Howell</em> &amp; <em>Hermès</em> &amp; <em>Alexander Wang</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t几乎每个品牌的模特都穿了高领衫，温暖、复古又优雅的百搭单品，可以单穿，可以外面加西装、风衣，或者再套一件毛衣。以体现材质的优良质感为主。\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t印花 ：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162534LRw65ThixFp7f2gj.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Louis Vuitton</em> &amp; <em>Alexander Wang</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162535WmjhkuCqxgvQGEzr.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Dior Homme</em> &amp; <em>Givenchy</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>低调的或者亮眼的印花，出现在丝绒西装外套上，挑人但穿好了实在很迷人。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t全黑色：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t一身黑这种万年经典，圣罗兰可能比较有发言权，可惜他们的模特实在是太……看下图自行感受吧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162538FcjN8Tyz0UnLMol3.jpg\" width=\"541\" height=\"536\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.99075786\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162539h6mcG0BKwPgkDznC.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"542\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t <em>Bottega Veneta</em> &amp; <em>Lemaire</em> &amp; <em>Givenchy</em>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t廓形挺括短夹克：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>让你看起来最有活力的一件单品，实用保暖还有型。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162540490nwOHeRxZCjG5p.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Lemaire</em> &amp; <span style=\"text-align:center;\"><em>Louis Vuitton</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162541WHEdjvIToD3thBY9.jpg\" width=\"907\" height=\"686\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75633958\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Calvin Klein</em>   &amp;   <em>Dolce &amp; Gabbana</em>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t中性：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\tFinally ，来到这一季绕不开的话题——女装男穿、雌雄共体各种女装元素的参与。这样开脑洞的表达，给了设计师太多空间。可能有一些裙装和粉色的设计，比较适合乐于“吸睛”的人群。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162542Uv5SQZK1JREmOq7g.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n"}